data.description: Welcome home to this updated, 4 bedroom/2.5 bath is a must see. You are welcomed into your two story foyer. Kitchen features quartz counters, custom cabinets,  stunning tile back splash, large pantry and patio doors leading out to deck. Family room with brick fireplace/insert and large windows to the backyard. All bathrooms were updated with design and storage in mind. Updates also include Premium Vinyl Siding (2020), roof (2013) and windows (2013). Gifford School District. Seller has a home warranty in place until 2027.
